    "voice": [
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_In_1",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "欢，欢，欢迎您！……老师！",
        "text_original": "い、い、いらっしゃいませ！ …先生！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/j6NJvh0hnGYtdpA8OXQ3dAZP17QtRoCR.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_In_2",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "好无聊啊…… ……呜啊！？您，您什么时候来的？！",
        "text_original": "暇だなぁ…。 …え、うわあ！？ い、いつから来てました？！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/rjJj7RCyyvEpEME0LghvBgTeDazSok9x.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Out_1",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "多谢您今天的惠顾！",
        "text_original": "ありがとうございました！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/JWx0cxWQMzoqa0y181RHu6Fb6B7GmF0p.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Out_2",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "欢迎您下次再来，老师！",
        "text_original": "また来てくださいね、先生！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/YfrgfpdUWeOuPnanksZqcvRlM3AXDKRl.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Talk_1",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "呀！请，请您别碰我的额头！",
        "text_original": "ひぁっ！お、おでこは 触らないでください！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/ttw5iZFHkkm2beokoywZRguxJnLWttEQ.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Talk_2",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "我，我觉得……执行任务，应该要做好充分的准备！",
        "text_original": "任務には…その、 じゅ、充分な準備が必要だと 思います！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/v2tUiyu7PHXCB52cITlGABMpdwnrZuy4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Talk_3",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "所以……还是建议您多买一点！大家都说，在我们店里买东西很划算！",
        "text_original": "ですから…いっぱい買った方が いいですよ！うちのお店の物は買った方が 絶対にお得ですって！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/PUciSJ3nsrxmwAKnN6HpZnQm4ievdHOs.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Talk_4",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "呃，老师，您一直这么盯着我看，我会不好意思的……！",
        "text_original": "あ、あの、そんなにじっと 見つめられると 困ってしまうのですが…！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/coalik6zTNxSvuKjwZk0ufYfa83nB4Ne.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Talk_5",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "可以请您……给我看一下大人的卡片吗？",
        "text_original": "大人のカード…見せていただいても よろしいでしょうか？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/ycbBe2uihqrXEoBTSU9WrTj23iqmKrem.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Talk_6",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "可，可是……我觉得我们店的价格真的很良心了！",
        "text_original": "で、ですが…うちのお店は！ すごく良心的なお値段ですから！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/Sl6P94fCjW7rPAoqZXEHjHfQN8xlSWyL.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "Sora_Shop_Talk_7",
        "category": "other",
        "text": "一天24小时，您随时都可以来光顾！毕竟这里算是便利店嘛！",
        "text_original": "24時間！いつでも訪問してください！ コンビニみたいなものですから！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E7%A9%BA/NPIcRpYMOJTe0ck2zI5uJmxPzop5cUDo.ogg"
      }
    ],
